## Open custom page

```json
{
  "aps": {
    "alert": {
      "title": "...",
      "subtitle": "...",
      "body": "...",
      "badge": 1
    }
  },
  "event": {
    "type": "custom",
    "uri": "order/status/36",
    "payload": {}
  },
  "src": {
    "type": "transactional",
    "id": "order_delivered"
  }
}
```

> For Android

```json
{
  "title": "...",
  "body": "...",
  "type": "transactional",
  "id": "order_delivered",
  "event": "{\"type\": \"custom\", \"uri\": \"order/status/36\", \"payload\": {}}"
}
```

Can be used to open any resource by custom data. For example for transactional messages to show order status.



